column5: Netflix is logged out. Fix it.
Stop sharing the pass with your friends then.
Bro send 500. I'm starving.
Ask Dad. I'm not a bank.
Who was that girl you were with at the station?
When? I wasn't at the station.
Blue jacket. Holding hands. Don't lie lol.
Fine. Keep your mouth shut. I'll send the money.
Money received. You're the best bhaiya ;)
Anjali is asking if we are coming home this weekend.
Tell her I have a special lab session.
Saw you again. Same girl. Different cafe.
What do you want now Aryan?
I need your old gaming monitor.
Deal. Take it next time you visit.
Enjoy the concert. Hope "the project" is fun.
Anjali looks suspicious. She was grilling me today.
What did you tell her?
Told her you were at the concert with Varun.
Dad's mad about the grades. Good luck bro.
